Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:46.18,small - white,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1685.333,780)}Game 10\NEast Round 1
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.50,0:05:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Harada is most probably holding a Pinzu (dots) Honisou
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.78,0:05:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So here, should he discard his 7 Sou (bamboo)?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.60,0:05:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If he discards the 7 Sou he's one from Tenpai
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.85,0:05:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Harada's still full of Pin (dot) tiles
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.35,0:06:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's careless he may yet deal into Hiroyuki's hand
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Only a Tatehon hand?(closed single suit)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.81,0:06:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This won't amount to a Mangan hand
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.05,0:06:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It gets him to Tenpai one turn faster
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.85,0:06:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,However
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.10,0:06:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If Hiroyuki draws a 1 or 4 Pin, he might just discard it
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.20,0:07:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like Harada's in Tenpai
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.55,0:07:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If he wins then the loss to this side should be large
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.35,0:07:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If Hiroyuki had discarded a 7 Sou from this hand
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.05,0:07:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd be in Tenpai now with this 1 Pin draw
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.85,0:07:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He missed the win, didn't he
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.18,0:07:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.65,0:07:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a mistake at all
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.65,0:07:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,hunh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.20,0:07:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.78,0:07:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Will change into an entirely DIFFERENT one
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.85,0:07:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A Jyunchan Ryanpeikou???
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.25,0:07:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,but to get that you'd need to draw another 9 Sou, and he's already using 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.05,0:07:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you could draw someting like that it would be the DEVIL'S OWN LUCK
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.80,0:07:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He's truly got no chance
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.55,0:07:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,My god...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.90,0:08:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,H-he DREW IT
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.30,0:08:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So, now they change
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.40,0:08:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether this hand will be completed is now entrusted to Ten
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.75,0:08:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.35,0:08:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten's discards show he's certainly got a large hand
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.25,0:08:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.20,0:08:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ipeikou Tsumo with 2 Dora
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A Mangan win
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.88,0:08:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiroyuki,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.55,0:08:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me get a little crazy here
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had a vision
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.85,0:08:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,of a pounding within the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.40,0:08:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,of a DRAGON
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.40,0:08:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,sunk deep underground
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Kan
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.75,0:09:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,His hand's all messed up
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.45,0:09:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,His chance for either Jyunchan or Ryanpeiko just vanished!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.25,0:09:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.95,0:09:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Akatsu is without doubt in Tenpai
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If he wins he could take out the East team
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.55,0:09:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus H. Christ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.10,0:10:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A typical slow SuuAnKou
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.90,0:10:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it no use at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.70,0:11:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Kan
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.45,0:11:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,THE DRAGON HAS SPLIT THE EARTH
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.55,0:12:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumo
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.85,0:12:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,SuuAnKou
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.20,0:12:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.70,0:12:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This SuuAnKou lowers Akagi's score by 8,000 points
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.70,0:12:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,but the other two are KNOCKED OUT AT ONE STROKE
